{
  "stem": "11882.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I knew of that from school, where we had lost all our students.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were there-- I think he was there three weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he came back three weeks later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was the night, strangely, that he had arrived, a few hours earlier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they had a dear friend, a doctor, an MD that was a friend of the family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was there with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a big courageous deal for him to associate with his former-- his friend, the Jewish man, because he was a marked man in that town, primarily because he was Jewish and also because he was supposed to be so rich.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he said, I don't know what Hitler has against me, said this poor man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know what Hitler has against me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I have always kept away from politics.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I am strictly apolitical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I like the things that Hitler does-- you know, the Autobahn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the only thing I don't like is his kraft durch freude.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That means strength through joy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And with that, Hitler financed the building of many big ships.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And to get the money out of everybody's pockets, he said it was for the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was for the people, of course, Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they could go on these wonderful trips to Rome in these KdF ships-- KdF ships, Kraft durch Freude.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had his file arranged alphabetically-- Australia, Brazil, it went right through the list of the countries that he was corresponding with, the diplomats of these countries to see if there would be any way that in such a country, if he got there-- he thought he could get there without any problem.",
      "word_count": 54
    }
  ],
